Package simzombie.engine.environment

Class Summary
Cell Environments are constructed of Cell objects Cells specifically contain data on whether or not their have boundaries at two entry/exit points - the northern wall and western wall.
CellReference CellReference is a utility class used for referring to a specific cell within the environment grid.
Environment Handles the environment of the simulation, including which agents are present in particular cells.
EnvironmentEditor The GUI component for editing environments (adding/removing walls)
EnvironmentPanel An extension of JPanel that displays a given Environment object.
